ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
Department of Citizenship and Immigration Act
SubjectDelivery of Direct and Indirect Services to Newcomers in Manitoba 2013-14 ** Agreements **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, to enter into TWO CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS with MANITOBA in order to provide transitional funding for ONE YEAR of delivery of direct and indirect services to newcomers.
